    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris et Filii et Spiritus Sancti. Anno Deo propicio pontificatus
                        domni <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/240">Iohannis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">summi pontificis et huniversalis pape</rs> in apostolica
                        sacratissima beati Petri apostoli Domini sede quinto, die tertiodecimo
                        mensis marcii, indictione tercia, foris civitatem <placeName
                            ref="#places/594">Ravenne</placeName>, in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3535">Sablonaria</placeName>, post tribunal palacii quod
                        olim construere iussit domnus <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/173">Hotto</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs>. Ea enim que iesta esse videntur in
                        futuris prolixisque temporibus memoriter retineri non possunt, quapropter
                        necesse est scripture vinculo anotari. Igitur dum resideret Deo annuente
                            <persName key="#Archbishops" ref="#people/1562">Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopus</rs><orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/223"> sancte <placeName ref="#places/43"
                                >Placentine</placeName> Ecclesie</orgName> in generali <rs
                            key="#Placitum/iudicatum">placito</rs>, simul cum eo <persName
                            key="#Bishops"><name ref="Hugo">Hugo</name></persName> gracia Dei <rs
                            key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches">sancte <placeName>Hansdeburgensis</placeName>
                            Ecclesie</orgName>, iussione domne <persName key="#Queen"
                            ref="#people/1525">Theofana</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">imperatricis</rs>, residentes et adstantes cum eis <rs
                            key="#Personal_rank">nobiles viri laudabilesque fama</rs>, nomina quorum
                        sunt hec, idest: <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Paulus"
                            >Paulus</name></persName> dativus, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> dativus, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Andreas de Utilis">Andreas</name></persName>
                        dativus de Utilis, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohannes</name></persName> dativus filius quondam <persName
                            key="#Consules"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Consules">consulis</rs> et alter <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Iohannes/Calcianpelle">Iohannes dativus
                            Calcianpelle</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Petrus de Traversaria">Petrus de Traversaria</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Paulus">Paulus</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        germani filii sui, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Paulus de Traversaria">Paulus de Traversaria</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        atque <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Deusdedit"
                            >Deusdedit</name></persName> filii sui, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Marquis/duke"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Consules"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Consules">consul</rs> et pater civitatis et Paulus et Petrus
                        germani filii quondam Pauli qui vocabatur de Traversaria, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Gherardus de Faraldo">Gerardus de
                                Farualdo</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Faraldus/Paulus">Farualdus qui vocatur Paulus</name></persName>
                        filius iamdicti Pauli iudicis, <persName key="#Witness #Consules"><name
                                ref="Petrus de Cristoduli">Petrus consul de
                            Cristoduli</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Consules"><name
                                ref="Gherardus">Gerardus</name></persName> consul, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes de Guandilo">Iohannes de
                                Guandilo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Vitalis">Vitalis</name></persName> filius quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Vitalis">Vitalis</name></persName> atque
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Constantinus de Lazario"
                                >Constantinus de Lazario</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Iohannes de Tenda">Iohannes de Tenda</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Maurizo">Mauricius</name></persName>
                        filius suus, <persName key="#Witness #Consules"><name
                                ref="Maurizo de Romano">Mauricius consul de Romano</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Paulus/Rastaneus">Paulus
                                Rastaneus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Tabellio"
                                ><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Tabellio"><name
                                ref="Apollinaris">Apollinaris</name></persName> tabellio et
                            <persName key="#Witness #Tabellio"><name ref="Aldus"
                            >Aldo</name></persName> tabellio et ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Tabellio"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        Deo largente tabellio civitatis Ravenne et alii quorum recordari non possum;
                        in eorum iamdictorum presencia reclamaverunt et interpellaverunt
                        suprascripti germani Paulus et Petrus filii quondam Pauli qui vocabatur de
                        Traversaria semel et bis et tercia vice de <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes/de Mariana">Iohanne qui vocatur de
                            Mariana</name></persName> et de <persName><name ref="Iohannes de Strata"
                                >Iohanne de Strata</name></persName> et de <persName><name
                                ref="Ghisulfus">Gisulfo</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Dominico</name></persName> germano suo de omni re
                        integra quam ipsi detinent in <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fundi" ref="#estates/2430">Scamno</geogName> et in <rs
                            key="#Fundi">fundo</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fundi" ref="#estates/2431">Lisiniano</geogName> et in <rs
                            key="#Fundi">fundo</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fundi" ref="#estates/2432">Peritulo</geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Fundi" ref="#estates/2433">Roveritulo</geogName>, sitis in <rs
                            key="#Fines">territorio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/2422"><placeName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#places/3515">Liviensis</placeName></geogName> et <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Fundi #Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1494">Sancte Marie in
                                <placeName key="#Fundi #Plebs" ref="#places/3536"
                                >Aqueducto</placeName></orgName>, ‘que res nobis pertinent et nobis
                        contendunt’. Hoc audito a predicto Iohanne archiepiscopo et ab Hugone
                        episcopo interpellati sunt suprascriptis iudicibus que de hoc lex esset. Et
                        ipsi <rs key="#Judge">iudices</rs> dixerunt: ‘Facite eos vocare per <rs
                            key="#Chancellor">publicum cancellarium</rs> in eodem placito’. Et ita
                        factum est. Et minime eos habere potuit. Item iam fati Iohannes
                        archiepiscopus et Hugo dixerunt ipsis iudicibus quid rectum esset de hoc.
                        Iudices vero dixerunt: ‘Postquam eos vocare fecistis et ad placitum non
                        venerunt, rectum est ut vos suprascriptis germanis Paulo et Petro de
                        suprascriptis rebus investiatis salva querela’. Et ita fecerunt per virgam
                        quam in suis detinebant manibus. Hoc autem facto apreenderunt manu <persName
                            key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Richulfus">Riculfum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarium</rs> et miserunt in manus iamdictorum
                        germanorum ut cum illis ad eas res pergeret et corporaliter illis exinde
                        investiret; deinde miserunt bandum super capita eorum ut nullus sit ausus
                        eis de illa re disvestire sine legali iudicio et qui facere presumpserit,
                        siat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">centum mancosos aureos</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem camere imperatricis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem ipsis germanis
                            eorumque heredibus</rs>. Hoc factum est sub die et mense, indictione
                        suprascripta tercia, foris civitatis Ravenne, in loco qui dicitur
                        Sablonaria, post tribunal palacii quod construere iussit domnus Hotto
                        imperator. Petrus Deo donante dativus in hac investicione et bandicione
                        interfui et subscripsi. Andreas Deo favente dativus in hac investicione ut
                        superius legitur interfui et subscripsi. Petrus filius quondam Petri
                        consullis in hac investicione ut superius legitur interfui.</ab>
                </div>
